parameters: \n<Katara>*pant*...*pant*...If I've made it this far...!

\n<Katara>...(There's no sign of them... I've completely shaken them
off! Now to deal with the coagulation crystal...)

\n<Katara>The barrier is completely gone!! I have no choice but to
throw it into the sea... No, there are monsters in the sea
too! I have to throw it as far away as possible, or it'll be
found immediately...

\n<Katara>Ugh...ughhhhh!!! No, I can't! I can't touch this anymore...
I feel nauseous...!!
\n<???>(You've done well, Katara.)
\n<Katara>Wh...who...? Whose voice...
\n<Cat Borrower>(It's me.)
\n<Katara>Huh...? Cat Borrower? The hand... spoke...?

\n<Cat Borrower>(Since you're borrowing a hand, of course there's someone
lending it to you, right? Fufufu♥ Did you think hands just
sprouted from nowhere?)

\n<Cat Borrower>(I will take the coagulation crystal and sink it to the
bottom of the distant sea, in a deep sea area devoid of
monsters. So don't worry anymore.)

\n<Cat Borrower>(Magic dissolves in water. Even a mass of malice like this
will eventually become part of the vast ocean over time and
naturally disappear.)

\n<Cat Borrower>(Ugh...this is quite a nasty piece of work. It feels
disgusting...)

\n<Cat Borrower>(The reason Chelsea couldn't use the Cat Borrower is that I
thought she didn't need it. She's a straight and strong girl
who doesn't get lost.)

\n<Cat Borrower>(However, you twins are different. Special twins. Innate
talent. Born status. There's a risk of becoming complacent
and arrogant due to your superiority over others, and
straying from the path.)

\n<Cat Borrower>(Katara... no, Wanz Wars. You were quite a handful, my
daughter.)
\n<Cat Borrower>(Katara... no, Louisham. You were quite a handful, my son.)
\n<Katara>Mo...Mother...?

\n<Cat Borrower>(But now you're alright. You've gone outside, interacted
with people, clashed with them, and even if you were led
astray, you didn't make mistakes and made it this far.)

\n<Cat Borrower>(There's nothing to worry about. Both Louisham and Wanz Wars
are my pride and joy.)

\n<Cat Borrower>(Seize the future with your own hands. This is the last time
I will lend you a hand.)
\n<Cat Borrower>(But I will always be watching over you. My dear children.)
\n<Katara>Ah...don't go...
\n<Katara>...

\n<Katara>Thank you for everything!! I can do it too! Because I'm your
child, Mom! I'll keep trying! I'll keep going!!

\n<Katara>Thank you for everything!! I'll try even harder!! Because
I'm a proud member of the Catfield family!

Afterwards, the horde of monsters including Terra lost sight
of the coagulation crystal and were mostly repelled by the
efforts of the Lumare Guard, with the survivors giving up
and leaving.

The damage to Dreen was severe, but reconstruction is
progressing smoothly with cooperation from Lumare.

Noblesse Count was imprisoned after his conspiracy was
exposed. The fact that he tried to bury the slum dwellers
alive was made public. However, there are still not a few
residents in the noble district who support him.

Habits are frightening things; despite everything that
happened, slum dwellers still drink during the day and
residents of the noble district still litter.

Just because they fought together once doesn't mean that
years of grudges were instantly resolved.

But things are steadily changing. Everyone, both those above
and those below, could feel it. Even if it's just a little,
they're trying to truly understand each other.
And as for us...
And as for us boys...
